column5: Fishing up at my trailer and caught half a dozen  bows on a blue fox spinner.
Sweet, any pics?  Any size to them?
dont have my phone i had the pics on but they ranged around 3 to 7 pounds

They were nice fish from what I can remember by the pics on his cell phone. He got them down river from me that day. Course I'm too lazy to walk down river,figures ! Hey Shinny just send the pics to me and I'll post them for ya
haha i kinda lost that phone so i cant
Too bad Dev. Theres always this fall for more pics.
oh ya thats gonna be a blast
